title: What are patients' overall experiences of out-of hours GP services?
analysis_commentary: The majority of patients are also happy with their overall experiences of out-of-hours GP services, but to a lesser extent than their overall experience of GP surgeries. Of the patients who responded in 2012/2013, 70% said their experience of out-of-hours GP services were very and fairly good and a similar proportion responded in the same way in 2011/2012.
